CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 17, 1956, pg. 30, reads: "Hail the Champs - There was plenty to cheer about for this happy group of Farrell High School cage stars at the Pitt Field House Monday night.  The reason for all the shouting was the Steelers' 48-41 victory over Monessen for the WPIAL Class A championship. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Farrell High School basketball team and coach cheering after winning WPIAL Class A championship, University of Pittsburgh Field House
